name: (Environmentally friendly) Drop Cards embedded with live wildflower seeds.
description:
Our New Environmentally friendly Drop Cards are “Physical” download cards filled with digital access to our carefully selected released & Unreleased Songs
Videos, Radio interviews, TV Footage, latest photos & Unseen Live performance footage. 

Our Drop cards are made out of 100% post-consumer junk mail and embedded with live wildflower seeds. After a card has been redeemed, it can be planted under a thin layer of soil, watered, and it will blossom into a garden of growth! Our dropcards expire after two years so you got plenty of time to get planting!

Our seeded drop cards are personally designed by Sarina Leah from Native Sun especially for you for that unique touch.

On Drop card’s you will find;
 
London's Freshest Hip Hop AfroSoul Duo Native Sun collaborate with KMT Freedom Teacher to bring you a compilation of Unreleased music, radio and TV Interviews, Exclusive footage of a  live band performance in Belgium, Multiple music videos, photoshoot & a short documentary.

Keep it movin MP3 feat Bocafloja
Faith Whosane Mp3 feat. Native Sun
Native Sun The anthem Mp3
G.M.O Mp3
Native Sun Live band performance in Belgium Video
Native Sun KMT Photoshoot by Bumi Thomas
Gallery of Dreams Music Video
Legacy Music Video
Lightness Of Happiness Music Video
Keep it movin Music Video feat Bocafloja
Native Sun EPK Video
Interview with Vox Africa TV Channel
KMT May project Video
Native and KMT Radio Show at SOAS Radio in London

Once you receive your drop card Please visit
www.dropcards.com/nativesunmuzik
